(259, 65, 'description', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I am an experienced programmer, gamer, and music enthusiast with a passion for innovation and problem-solving. Throughout my years, I actively participated in numerous projects, competitions, and collaborated with top programming companies to work on fascinating, diverse projects that can bring meaningful impacts towards their users.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I am eager to continue my journey, building on academic and practical experiences, and focus on multiple aspects of computer science such as AI and Game Development.</p>'),
