(2195, 237, 'list_2_content', 'https://youtu.be/Pr5avChfRf4?si=FvAfAZU965DlZght\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating a self-driving car became my mission because I witnessed the persistent issue of impaired and intoxicated driving, especially after holiday gatherings and parties. Heartbreaking incidents resulted from individuals operating vehicles with high levels of alcohol in their system, exceeding legal limits. My journey began in 7th grade, embarking on my first AI programming project, which was applied to the self-driving car project designed by GotIt\'s Founder and Chief Architect, Gabi Zuniga. During this time, I had the invaluable opportunity to learn from the experts at Got It Inc. The future expanded before me as I designed an AI-based delivery robot that autonomously followed pre-programmed routes. The concept of driverless cars was relatively new in Vietnam, and the revelation that a robot could operate independently using AI technology surprised many. My story of creating a self-driving car as an 7th-grade student opened doors to meeting numerous experts in Vietnam\'s technology industry. I hope it serves as motivation for young tech enthusiasts, demonstrating that it\'s never too early or too late to pursue their dreams.</span>'),
