(6143, 423, 'list_0_content', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cy2g9LqVjpM\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Having grappled with the IELTS exam, particularly the Reading test, I am driven to support others on their journey through the IELTS Reading Assistant. Among the four essential language skills, the Reading test demands a high level of English proficiency to understand complex texts within a limited time frame. Mastering this skill can be a daunting and perplexing task, as students encounter diverse teaching approaches from various instructors. To address this issue, I have developed this product to aid students in selecting the most effective learning method for conquering the IELTS test.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The product\'s internal model is designed to analyze user input, which includes an IELTS Reading Passage and its associated questions, in order to generate answers. The system then presents users with multiple choice questions based on its approaches to answering these questions. This approach helps individuals to incorporate these strategies into their IELTS practice, ultimately enhancing their test performance.</p>'),
(6144, 423, '_list_0_content', 'field_653e58a91065a'),
(6145, 423, 'list_0_button', 'SEE PRODUCT'),
(6146, 423, '_list_0_button', 'field_653e58a91069c'),
(6147, 423, 'list_0_link', 'https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1E6-BmepLiAjhK9B3NmYAmkF15mMkT0NJ1fMH8QWLmls/edit'),
