(6950, 449, '_title_2', 'field_653e316dcd130'),
(6951, 449, 'description_2', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>About Got It:</strong> A technology startup by Mr.Hung Tran in Silicon Valley, USA.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Website:<span style=\"color: #fffce1;\"> <a class=\"vyn9Qd\" style=\"color: #fffce1;\" href=\"http://www.got-it.ai/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">www.got-it.ai</a></span></strong></span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a remarkable journey that began when I was just in the 7th grade, I took the extraordinary step of creating my own resume. This decision ultimately led to my becoming the youngest and sole software engineering intern accepted at Got It, Inc., and holds the distinction of being the only intern of my age group in Vietnam.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
