(210, 1, '2023-10-29 15:49:08', '2023-10-29 15:49:08', '<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-211 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/366586477_197940783271746_2464261500335916016_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1178\" />\n\n<b>1.Workshop AI Experience:The Age of Artificial Intelligence</b>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the context of the ongoing efforts within the education and scientific communities, the Online STEM Topic Workshop took place on June 11th, attracting the participation of hundreds of enthusiasts and those interested in the field of STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics) from around the world. The event provided a day full of information, knowledge sharing, and learning opportunities from reputable speakers in the field.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Speaker Tran Minh Quang kicked off the event with an engaging presentation on the importance of STEM in modern and future life. He emphasized the decisive role of STEM in addressing global challenges and exploring new potentials.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The workshop concluded with an interactive session with the audience, allowing them to ask questions and exchange opinions with the speakers. The event helped create an open environment for sharing knowledge and connecting individuals interested in STEM.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In a world filled with challenges and opportunities, the Online STEM Topic Workshop, featuring top speakers, has contributed to the advancement of this field, and it is hoped that it will continue to pave the way for new developments in the future.</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-213 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Frame-1057.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1539\" height=\"753\" />\n\n<strong>2.<b>STEMPIRE Science Day 2023- Science Exhibition</b></strong>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The STEMpire Club was established with a mission to popularize STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, and Mathematics) and engineering sciences among passionate and curious students. We also aspire to make meaningful contributions to our community and connect with like-minded students. Simply put, we aim to create an environment where students can satisfy their scientific passions.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In pursuit of this goal, our club members collaborated to develop a program that included an exhibition showcasing scientific and engineering products and a collaborative effort to build a library with Phan Thiết Middle School.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Through these activities, STEMpire Club aimed to provide an incredible experience for the participating students. They had the opportunity to use and experience scientific and technological products like automated robots, electronic circuits, and artificial intelligence systems, all guided by STEMpire Club members. Notably, after experiencing these scientific products, STEMpire Club gifted Phan Thiết Middle School a model of a smart solar-powered house, constructed, designed, and programmed by our very own club members.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Furthermore, STEMpire Club was pleased to provide the school with English books and a desktop computer, all in an effort to support the school in building its library. We hope that this support will aid the school and its students in more effectively engaging with STEM subjects and sparking a passion for learning, research, and exploration in the field of science and engineering.</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>3.<span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\">Visit Tuyen Quang Hydroelectric Plant</span></strong>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The visit to the Tuyen Quang hydropower plant was truly an incredible and memorable experience for me. Right from the beginning, we were able to witness significant structures such as water reservoirs and the processing plant. Our expert guide explained how the machinery operates and how it generates electrical energy.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The most remarkable part of the tour was when we got up close and personal with the working turbines. The feeling of seeing hydropower in action, transforming water into electricity, is beyond words. It deepened our understanding of the necessity of this technology and the vital role it plays in providing electricity to millions of people.</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thanks to this trip, we gained a more profound insight into the electricity industry and renewable energy sources. We left feeling inspired and more conscious of the importance of environmental conservation and optimizing the use of renewable energy sources.</span>', 'Co-Founder of  STEMPIRE Club <br> (Nov 2022 - Now)', 'In the context of the ongoing efforts within the education and scientific communities, the Online STEM Topic Workshop took place on June 11th, attracting the participation of hundreds of enthusiasts and those interested in the field of STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics) from around the world. The event provided a day full of information, knowledge sharing, and learning opportunities from reputable speakers in the field.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '170-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-10-29 15:49:08', '2023-10-29 15:49:08', '', 170, 'http://localhost/trasua/?p=210', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
