launch a small campaign, a simple yet impactful action – planting an additional tree in all the gardens, balconies, schoolyards, offices, which we call \"Bringing Back the Green.\"\r\n\r\nAt our first destination, Greenwave collaborated with three projects to organize a Children\'s Day event and gave nearly 50 pots of plants and 50 gifts to children with specific disabilities, particularly at the Thuy An Functional Rehabilitation Center for People with Disabilities in Ba Vi.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-168 size-full\" src=\"/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/detail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1120\" height=\"268\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Green Land Returns Event</strong>\r\n\r\nWith our first series of activities, I and the Greenwave team aimed to launch a small campaign, a simple yet impactful action – planting an additional tree in all the gardens, balconies, schoolyards, offices, which we call \"Bringing Back the Green.\"\r\n\r\nAt our first destination, Greenwave collaborated with three projects to organize a Children\'s Day event and gave nearly 50 pots of plants and 50 gifts to children with specific disabilities, particularly at the Thuy An Functional Rehabilitation Center for People with Disabilities in Ba Vi.', 'President · UPBEAT<br>(Oct 2021 - Sep 2023)', 'A self-driving car trained by thousands of video recordings,  driving and turning automatically based on a path which was my first AI product I created in my career path in technology. I applied to a self-driving car project designed by Founder GotIt and chief architect Gabi Zuniga in 2016', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '166-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-10-29 16:10:22', '2023-10-29 16:10:22', '', 166, 'http://localhost/trasua/?p=221', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
