(324, 1, '2023-10-30 17:04:12', '2023-10-30 17:04:12', '<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-196 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/352198155_761321225780566_2282037430624259009_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1367\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>1.Gree</strong><strong>n Land Returns Event</strong></h2>\r\nWith our first series of activities, I and the Greenwave team aimed to launch a small campaign, a simple yet impactful action – planting an additional tree in all the gardens, balconies, schoolyards, offices, which we call \"Bringing Back the Green.\"\r\n\r\nAt our first destination, Greenwave collaborated with three projects to organize a Children\'s Day event and gave nearly 50 pots of plants and 50 gifts to children with specific disabilities, particularly at the Thuy An Functional Rehabilitation Center for People with Disabilities in Ba Vi.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-198\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_7197.tif\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-198\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_7197.tif\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-199 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_7197.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1399\" height=\"928\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>2.Trash\'s Journey Event</strong></h2>\r\nMaking a stop at the fair combined with the PLASTIVAL plastic exhibition is an ideal choice to create a space filled with colors, where children can have fun during the weekend and unleash their creativity in recycling plastic products.\r\n\r\nThrough this event, Greenwave aims to provide motivation for everyone to join hands in environmental protection, recycling, and transforming unique plastic recycling models, thereby helping the environment come back to life, greener than ever before\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;