(465, 1, '2023-11-02 03:06:53', '2023-11-02 03:06:53', '<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-211 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/366586477_197940783271746_2464261500335916016_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1178\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>1.Workshop AI Experience:\r\nThe Age of Artificial Intelligence</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the context of the ongoing efforts within the education and scientific communities, the Online STEM Topic Workshop took place on June 11th, attracting the participation of hundreds of enthusiasts and those interested in the field of STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics) from around the world. The event provided a day full of information, knowledge sharing, and learning opportunities from reputable speakers in the field.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Speaker Tran Minh Quang kicked off the event with an engaging presentation on the importance of STEM in modern and future life. He emphasized the decisive role of STEM in addressing global challenges and exploring new potentials.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The workshop concluded with an interactive session with the audience, allowing them to ask questions and exchange opinions with the speakers. The event helped create an open environment for sharing knowledge and connecting individuals interested in STEM.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a world filled with challenges and opportunities, the Online STEM Topic Workshop, featuring top speakers, has contributed to the advancement of this field, and it is hoped that it will continue to pave the way for new developments in the future.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-213 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Frame-1057.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1539\" height=\"753\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>2.STEMPIRE Science Day 2023\r\nScience Exhibition</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The STEMpire Club was established with a mission to popularize STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, and Mathematics) and engineering sciences among passionate and curious students. We also aspire to make meaningful contributions to our community and connect with like-minded students. Simply put, we aim to create an environment where students can satisfy their scientific passions.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In pursuit of this goal, our club members collaborated to develop a program that included an exhibition showcasing scientific and engineering products and a collaborative effort to build a library with Phan Thiết Middle School.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Through these activities, STEMpire Club aimed to provide an incredible experience for the participating students. They had the opportunity to use and experience scientific and technological products like automated robots, electronic circuits, and artificial intelligence systems, all guided by STEMpire Club members. Notably, after experiencing these scientific products, STEMpire Club gifted Phan Thiết Middle School a model of a smart solar-powered house, constructed, designed, and programmed by our very own club members.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Furthermore, STEMpire Club was pleased to provide the school with English books and a desktop computer, all in an effort to support the school in building its library. We hope that this support will aid the school and its students in more effectively engaging with STEM subjects and sparking a passion for learning, research, and exploration in the field of science and engineering.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-400 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Frame-1056-10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1499\" height=\"730\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>3.<span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\">Visit Tuyen Quang Hydroelectric Plant</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The visit to the Tuyen Quang hydropower plant was truly an incredible and memorable experience for me. Right from the beginning, we were able to witness significant structures such as water reservoirs and the processing plant. Our expert guide explained how the machinery operates and how it generates electrical energy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The most remarkable part of the tour was when we got up close and personal with the working turbines. The feeling of seeing hydropower in action, transforming water into electricity, is beyond words. It deepened our understanding of the necessity of this technology and the vital role it plays in providing electricity to millions of people.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanks to this trip, we gained a more profound insight into the electricity industry and renewable energy sources. We left feeling inspired and more conscious of the importance of environmental conservation and optimizing the use of renewable energy sources.</p>', 'Co-Founder of  STEMPIRE Club (Nov 2022 - Now)', 'In the context of the ongoing efforts within the education and scientific communities, the Online STEM Topic Workshop took place on June 11th, attracting the participation of hundreds of enthusiasts and those interested in the field of STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics) from around the world. The event provided a day full of information, knowledge sharing, and learning opportunities from reputable speakers in the field.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '170-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-11-02 03:06:53', '2023-11-02 03:06:53', '', 170, 'http://localhost/trasua/?p=465', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(466, 1, '2023-11-02 03:07:03', '2023-11-02 03:07:03', '<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-220 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Frame-1061-.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1539\" height=\"730\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong> 1.Christmas music show \"The Light\"</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Upbeat has been and will always be a source of immense pride for me. I\'ll never forget our very first public show at Purple Blues during Christmas, where we performed for a remarkable 2 hours and even took multiple song requests! It was such an enjoyable and memorable time. I\'m thrilled that we managed to have so much fun during a charity show. What\'s even more exciting is that we went on to host a SECOND charity show, which was an absolute blast in every sense of the word. Upbeat will forever hold a special place in my heart, rent-free. It marks my first live performance, in front of a diverse audience, alongside my friends.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Behind every live performance on the stage, the Upbeat band, comprising seven talented and charismatic individuals, will be the ambassadors of vibrant melodies and colorful sounds, promising spontaneity and musical brilliance.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As with all of Upbeat\'s projects, \"The Light Show\" is a fundraising endeavor through ticket sales. Upbeat commits to allocating all proceeds from the concert to contribute to the welfare of underprivileged children.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Upbeat\'s journey is one of music, camaraderie, and the joy of giving back, and it is an experience that I will cherish deeply.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-222 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/IMG_1304-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>2.Performance of Dan Tinh &amp; Then Singing at the Vietnamese National Academy Of Music.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the lyrical verses of the Tày people\'s \"Mùa hoa lê\" Then song, which I would loosely translate as \"In our village, the pear blossoms bloom, sparkling waters, the stream sings with delight,\" the joyful lyrics resonate with the gentle melodies of the Tính tẩu (Tày folk music) amidst the backdrop of Hanoi\'s landscapes. <i>Then </i>singing has the power to dispel the chill of winter and transport listeners across the high mountains to the majestic landscapes of the Northwest.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The enchanting charm of Then singing lies in its simplicity, sincerity, accessibility, and emotive qualities. Listening to Then is an instant source of joy and delight. Moreover, the pure and poetic lyrics of Then depict the beauty of nature, love, and the homeland, often leaving one utterly captivated.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">UpBeat regularly participates in musical exchanges, collaborating with students, enthusiasts, and the Tày ethnic community at the National Academy of Music in Vietnam. Through our involvement, we hope to not only preserve and promote the Then tradition for those who cherish it but also actively engage with and perform at events organized by the Tày community in the capital.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">With these initiatives, UpBeat aspires to connect and share the beauty of Then music, transcending boundaries and preserving the rich cultural heritage of the Tày people, and extending it to a broader audience, bringing the world closer to the enchanting rhythms of Tày folk music.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-224 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Frame-1123123u.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1539\" height=\"730\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>3.A tour and performance of Dan Tinh\r\nThen singing at Homestay Trieu Cuong</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I organized a cultural immersion trip for UpBeat Club members to provide them with a deep understanding of the Tày ethnic culture. The lush green surroundings, simple and peaceful way of life, and unique cultural aspects of the Tày people left a profound impression on everyone who visited this place.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Traveling along winding, picturesque roads and observing stilt houses nestled on the hillside, beneath the shade of cool trees, one could sense the serene life of the local inhabitants. Thượng Lâm Commune is not only renowned for its vast terraced fields but also as one of the cradles of the traditional Then singing style of the Tày ethnic group. Here, almost everyone can sing a few lines of Then songs, with many children as young as 6 or 7 years old participating in local Then singing clubs and Tính music ensembles within their village and commune.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">These young enthusiasts eagerly learn and strive to sing beautifully and authentically because it\'s a source of pride for their ethnic community. In the autumn, the atmosphere in the Thái Hải village is refreshing and mild. Sitting in a local wine house, listening to the Then song \"Tuyen Quang yêu thương,\" sung from the heart and filled with the emotions of the locals, with a cup of fragrant, sticky rice wine in hand, one can feel the rustic yet profound sentiments of the people living in this region.</p>', 'President · UPBEAT (Oct 2021 - Sep 2023)', 'Upbeat has been and will always be a source of immense pride for me. I’ll never forget our very first public show at Purple Blues during Christmas, where we performed for a remarkable 2 hours and even took multiple song requests! It was such an enjoyable and memorable time. I’m thrilled that we managed to have so much fun during a charity show.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '166-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-11-02 03:07:03', '2023-11-02 03:07:03', '', 166, 'http://localhost/trasua/?p=466', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(467, 1, '2023-11-02 03:55:01', '2023-11-02 03:55:01', '<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-196 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/352198155_761321225780566_2282037430624259009_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1367\" />\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>1.Gree</strong><strong>n Land Returns Event</strong></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">With our first series of activities, I and the Greenwave team aimed to launch a small campaign, a simple yet impactful action – planting an additional tree in all the gardens, balconies, schoolyards, offices, which we call \"Bringing Back the Green.\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">At our first destination, Greenwave collaborated with three projects to organize a Children\'s Day event and gave nearly 50 pots of plants and 50 gifts to children with specific disabilities, particularly at the Thuy An Functional Rehabilitation Center for People with Disabilities in Ba Vi.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-377 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Frame-1056-6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1499\" height=\"730\" />\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>2.Trash\'s Journey Event</strong></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Making a stop at the fair combined with the PLASTIVAL plastic exhibition is an ideal choice to create a space filled with colors, where children can have fun during the weekend and unleash their creativity in recycling plastic products.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Through this event, Greenwave aims to provide motivation for everyone to join hands in environmental protection, recycling, and transforming unique plastic recycling models, thereby helping the environment come back to life, greener than ever before</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-380 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/trasua/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Frame-1056-8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1499\" height=\"730\" />\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\"><strong>3.Green Land Returns Event</strong></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">With the desire to contribute a small part in propagating useful jobs for society to many people. The fact that we received the support of everyone attending is a joy as well as a great source of motivation for us to strive and contribute to make the project a success.In particular, we collected more than 20kg of plastic and donated all the trees to all of you.</p>', 'Founder & President · Greenwave Club (Dec 2021 - Now)', 'With our first series of activities, I and the Greenwave team aimed to launch a small campaign, a simple yet impactful action – planting an additional tree in all the gardens, balconies, schoolyards, offices, which we call \"Bringing Back the Green.\"', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '171-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-11-02 03:55:01', '2023-11-02 03:55:01', '', 171, 'http://localhost/trasua/?p=467', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
